Create a fun and functional outdoor space with our 5-piece Kids Round Dining and Play Table Set, paired with our Kids Plastic Adirondack Chairs. Made from durable, kid-friendly HDPE material, this set is perfect for both playtime and mealtime, offering UV and fade resistance to keep the vibrant color intact. The table features a reinforced design for added stability, while the Adirondack chairs and table are designed with smooth edges for safety and all-weather resistance. Complete your family set and enjoy a charming, durable addition to your outdoor space.

While we strive to accurately represent product colors, please be aware that actual colors may vary slightly due to individual screen settings and lighting conditions.
